<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī prathuvīvallabha ma
<lb n="2" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> jādhirāja paramēsvara
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> mabhaṭṭaraka śrīmatkannara
